in Rio.</i>

67
00:07:36,664 --> 00:07:40,098
Here! Buy some new balls.

68
00:07:41,662 --> 00:07:45,096
<i>But they were just amateurs.</i>

69
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:51,962
<i>—Even my brother, Goose.
—Rocket, give this money to dad.</i>

70
00:07:54,092 --> 00:07:56,395
