02:03:24,752 --> 02:03:28,316
—Put fucking Nightowl on there.
—And Croquet.

1367
02:03:28,533 --> 02:03:30,011
Leonard, too, he owes me money.

1368
02:03:30,315 --> 02:03:32,227
And China-Man,
he thinks he’s hot stuff.

1369
02:03:32,401 --> 02:03:35,400
—And Claudio.
—Where’s Giant?

1370
02:03:35,704 --> 02:03:38,399
Come on, Giant!

1371
02:03:52,784 --> 02:03:56,521
<i>I forgot to say,
my name isn’t Rocket anymore.</i>

1372
02:03:56,695 --> 02:03:58,998
<i>I am now Wilson Rodrigues …</i>

1373
02:03:59,172 --> 02:04:00,867
<i>photographer.</i>

1374
02:04:21,945 --> 02:04:23,814
<i>Manuel Machado,
a.k.a. Knockout Ned …</i>

1375
02:04:23,988 --> 02:04:27,030
<i>was hospitalized after
being wounded by Li’l Zé’s gang.</i>

1376
02:04:27,247 --> 02:04:30,159
<i>On leaving the hospital,
our reporter interviewed him.</i>

1377
02:04:30,420 --> 02:04:33,418
<i>Many have died.
Mostly innocent people.</i>

1378
02:04:33,592 --> 02:04:37,330
<i>Just knowing me is enough …</i>

1379
02:04:37,460 --> 02:04:41,371
<i>just being my friend …</i>

1380
02:04:41,545 --> 02:04:45,543
<i>If he thinks someone knows me,
he’ll kill them.</i>

1381
02:04:45,761 --> 02:04:47,586
<i>The police don’t go in there?</i>

1382
02:04:47,803 --> 02:04:53,149
<i>They go after me, not him.</i>

1383
02:04:53,410 --> 02:04:58,364
<i>I’ve been in jail three times,
while he goes on …</i>

1384
02:04:58,538 --> 02:05:01,102
<i>killing undisturbed.</i>

1385
02:05:01,319 --> 02:05:04,057
<i>And they don’t arrest him.</i>

1386
02:05:04,405 --> 02:05:06,969
<i>Knockout Ned says
the war will continue.</i>

1387
02:05:07,143 --> 02:05:12,010
<i>Police Chief Guedes has promised to
arrest both gangs in the City of God.</i>
